<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0385001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0385001">Samantacchadana（徧蓋）。</note>
<note n="0388001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0388001">Araññasatta（森林有情）。</note>
<note n="0390001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0390001">以上十偈半與前第一八七耶伽欽提陀長老所唱之偈，大致相同。</note>
<note n="0391002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0391002">Abbuda（濁垢）。</note>
<note n="0391003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0391003">Nirabuda（滅濁）。</note>
